                                                <div class="checkbox">
                                                    <label>
                                                        <input type="checkbox">
                                                        Negotiable </label>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>


                                        

                                        <div class="well">
                                            <h3><i class=" icon-certificate icon-color-1"></i> Make your Ad Premium
                                            </h3>

                                            <p>Premium jobs help promote their service by getting their ads more
                                                visibility with more
